name: NYDailyNews
text:
Brooklyn Assembly candidate Emily Gallagher admitted to mooning a couple having sex when she was 19.

According to a post she wrote, she spotted a couple having sex through a window and stopped to watch, then mooned them when they noticed.

name: NYDailyNews
text:
Former Jets bust Christian Hackenberg is trying to play pro baseball.

His coach said he hit 92 mph with his fastball, but is consistently at 90.

“I know how hard it is to hit a baseball," Hackenberg said, "but I have the arm talent.”

name: NYDailyNews
text:
The billionaires who own the 30 MLB teams were never negotiating with their players.

They are getting the joke of a short season they wanted all along — the bare minimum number of games the owners are willing to finance.
